trans-unit.target: Specifica il tipo di contenitore dei controlli dei dati.

trans-unit.source: Item containers holds item containers that implement the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.IDataBoundItemControl> interface, such as <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DetailsView> or <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.FormView> controls.
trans-unit.target: Elemento contenitori di elementi contiene contenitori che implementano il <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.IDataBoundItemControl> interfaccia, ad esempio <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DetailsView> o <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.FormView> controlli.

trans-unit.source: List containers hold list containers that implement the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.IDataBoundListControl> interface, such as <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ListView>, <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.GridView>, or <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Repeater> controls.
trans-unit.target: Elenco contenitori contenitori di elenco che implementano il <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.IDataBoundListControl> interfaccia, ad esempio <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ListView>, <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.GridView>, o <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Repeater> controlli.

trans-unit.source: Indicates an item container that implements the <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.WebControls.IDataBoundItemControl" /> interface, such as a <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DetailsView" /> control or a <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.WebControls.FormView" /> control.
trans-unit.target: Indica un contenitore di elementi che implementa l'interfaccia <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.WebControls.IDataBoundItemControl" />, ad esempio un controllo <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DetailsView" /> o un controllo <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.WebControls.FormView" />.

trans-unit.source: Indicates a list container that implements the <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.WebControls.IDataBoundListControl" /> interface, such as a <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ListView" /> control, a <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.WebControls.GridView" /> control, or a <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Repeater" /> control.
trans-unit.target: Indica un contenitore List che implementa l'interfaccia <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.WebControls.IDataBoundListControl" />, ad esempio un controllo <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ListView" />, un controllo <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.WebControls.GridView" /> o un controllo <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Repeater" />.
